                <h1>When Did Diet Coke Launch?</h1>
                <p>Diet Coke was launched in 1982 as a low-calorie alternative to the beloved Coca-Cola. It was the first extension of the Coke brand and quickly gained popularity. Known for its unique flavor and distinct packaging, Diet Coke became a staple in the beverage industry and has since evolved with various flavors and formulations.</p>
